high_descs: Turn left and then right from the center of the room.
Pick up the green sponge from the bath tub.
From your back side turn left and bank left.
At the bathroom sink drop in the sponge itself.
turn the on the water and fill with water.
With the sink empty pick up the wet sponge and drop it down back into the tub.
anns.task_desc: To wet a sponge, as to prepare the tub for cleaning.

high_descs: Turn around and go towards the cabinet.  Turn right and go to the tub.
Pick up the green sponge in the tub.
Turn around.  Go to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink.  Turn the water on.  Turn the water off.   Pick up the sponge out of the sink.
Turn around.  Then go to the right to the tub.
Put the sponge in the tub to the left of the toy.
anns.task_desc: Get the sponge, get it wet to put in the tub.

high_descs: at desk, turn right towards the tub.
at tub, pick up green soap.
Turn water on in sink, wash green soap.
Take soap off the sink, place back into the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Get green soap from tub, rinse it in sink, place back into tub.
